  "lock_statement": "Artificial intelligence should be evaluated according to its ability to preserve and expand both human participation and the physical conditions that make participation possible. AI creates value by carrying informational burdens, but informational gains alone do not constitute stewardship gains. The highest role of AI is stewardship: preserving recoverable human futures through simultaneous protection of participation, physical viability, future accessibility, and recoverability across generations."
